Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难不成— 是我啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}该怎么办啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别想了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别再深究这事了 雾岛海人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天那样才不是对学姐告白了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就像前天那样 学姐不是也没反应过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放平常心哦 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.92,0:02:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可比海人年长 不振作怎么能行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像平常那样做好早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后稍微努力一下 试着做个便当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是和学姐同住在这屋檐下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.52,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要保持平常心哦 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常至终 和往常一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常心 平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想做就能做到的 要有自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…这么说有点怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不如说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}NO！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早…早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.80,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天…天气真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天看来会放晴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}马上就要…期末考了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我读书不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是这样吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上吃了啥我都不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你这么早起真是难得一见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}偶…偶尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和你走散了…然后也没去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我才是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说回来 都是柠檬学姐和美樱不好！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天我诚恳道歉了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.97,0:03:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对了 听我说啊 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天不单是柠檬学姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗和美樱也去偷窥了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.45,0:04:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}发生什么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你说“什么”是想指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为你态度和平常不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吗…没这回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我超正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天…你去轻井泽了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.47,0:04:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去买东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学也在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在轻井泽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.81,0:04:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雾岛同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然是…让她困扰了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不会…没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只是因为突然了点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.17,0:05:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以内心有些动摇了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我其实也…对海人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好~两情相悦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.90,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不喜欢搞基
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是我的反应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}刚才一夏学姐拜托我给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说“帮我拿给小海”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐她？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}人家难得给你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊…哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只是在假设啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A雄君向B子酱说了像是告白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然后 B子酱一言不发的回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再然后B子酱对A雄君的态度就变得有些不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请问B子酱的心理状态是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.42,0:06:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A美酱听到B太君说了像是告白的话后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}由于太过惊讶就从那里逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请问A美酱应该采取什么态度？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}应该做个答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顺便问一下 A美酱觉得B太君怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定不是讨厌他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}甚至觉得他有点可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就答应咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这问题…才没有这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这是因为…A美酱她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会离开这个小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}B子酱确实觉得很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过无法确定她是觉得很烦恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还是需要些时间来考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我觉得A雄君还是不要急于得到答覆来得好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不要急…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在偷懒 被我发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了？累了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个啊…早上忘了问你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天我们走散之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你去干嘛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也没办法 只好回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.14,0:08:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你有找我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哎呀 这不是雾岛同学和谷川同学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么啊…原来是柠檬学姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这招呼真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明看到魅力十足的年长女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正展现着妖艳的泳装姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}“妖艳”什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只不过是学校泳衣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要集合咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我们走吧 柠檬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}A美酱似乎有个叫C子酱的情敌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶？你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道说 你还在和贵月学姐闹别扭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.39,0:08:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你得振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然说 因为贵月学姐是外国人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在交流方面可能会有许多问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐孤身一人来到这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或许正感到不安啊…寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在这方面海人应该多关照她一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 正如谷川所说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我只顾着想自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我觉得肯为他人着想的海人很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 C子酱在猛踩地雷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}C子酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.79,0:09:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我得振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}振作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一夏学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什…什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}关于昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我作出了奇怪的反应真对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我没有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 我们回归往常那样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回归往常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就用这招打破现状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我要做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不做不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想做！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么欲求不满吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那是当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真 真奈美姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那要我来和你做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什 么 都 可 以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}搞不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}装什么纯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海 我正要去购物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来陪我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反对无效 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:10:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你真是明鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人同学你这份心意让我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我们才相识不久
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以 能不能给我一点时间再作答覆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会在好好考虑过海人的各方面后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好的做出答覆的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那之前 让我们像往常一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我会听从学姐的意见的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就这么跟他说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.90,0:11:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那位女性是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这…这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}昨天才向我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}虽然我没有好好答覆他也有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没过一天 竟然就和别的女人约会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难以置信！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}烦恼着的我简直就像笨蛋一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 随他的便了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}用连环让我进行跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\fscx50\fscy50\pos(524,664)}linkage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这次再不回应我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}后果很严重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音 这是因为 那个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐拜托了我要照顾海人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}被｢拜托了”而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}仅此而已 仅此而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这个和这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要买这么多吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这次是长期战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那么 接着要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等…真奈美姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明明就心里偷着乐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.11,0:13:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.07,0:13:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}竟 竟然那么大胆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.59,0:13:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海 想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么样 好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…哦…呃 完美到极致了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.34,0:13:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以快点买了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如何 我比那个叫一夏的女生要好多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那种告白了也不答覆的女生 还是忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我先去洗个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你随便喝个茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要一起洗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打从心底拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去之后得和学姐说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学…学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这种小事无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别问了 先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你就这么想待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 应该先打声招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.79,0:15:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.09,0:15:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.05,0:15:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么我会这么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个 学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}干什么吵吵闹闹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这女生是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.86,0:15:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难道是阿海的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是受他姐姐之托来照顾海人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}七海拜托的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以不能让海人留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.58,0:16:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有什么 不是恋爱自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你看起来比他可大上不少
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}年龄不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人还是高中生呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}爱总是伴随着阻碍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真奈美姐你说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人你闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你还不懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你是电灯泡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我有保护海人的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}仅仅如此？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}仅仅是这样的理由就让你擅自闯进别人家里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太不合理了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多该从实招来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你来这里真正的目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}才没什么真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.34,0:16:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海 这孩子真是相当迟钝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.80,0:16:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.80,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 算了随便你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这也是年轻人的乐子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.35,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你怎么又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}咦 海 连一夏学姐都来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是姐姐带来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那随便坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}话说 你别穿成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}去换衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.08,0:17:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}石垣同学 那个…你说“姐姐”是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}还没介绍过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是我姐姐小仓真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小仓…可姓氏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因为结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:40.97,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}在日本结婚后妇随夫姓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐姐她一和老公吵架就跑回来发牢骚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这次绝饶不了他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}为什么吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那家伙擅自就把我录的节目删了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无聊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可是很期待的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了好了 快回智叔那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就算他下跪也不原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.53,0:18:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}这回真是受够他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你到底是帮谁的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}正义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起 真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}说回来 我才是让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}总的来说还是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.67,0:18:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没事 都怪真奈美姐说了些让人误解的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}会那样也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呐 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}让我赔礼补偿你吧 干什麽都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么都行？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那个时候 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其实是很想问的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}请告诉我昨天的答覆 我在你心里是什么地位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:19:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我读书不太好 学姐…能教教我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.93,0:19:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我尽量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.26,0:19:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那里拼写错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那里不是“E”而是“I”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}英语做完了以后是数学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 该睡觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天还要上学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}离期末考试没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照你这成绩 你姐姐会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}至少要考到平均分以上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}只要及格就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你首先态度就不端正
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是你叫我教你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}来 做题目
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.34,0:19:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是没说就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.60,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}這裡他說的是前輩（せんぱい）的後半部分和おっぱい 胸部的尾音相同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我的姐啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 胸部？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}没想到学姐还有那种性格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}贵月学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐 现在是午休啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}边吃边学啊 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 好辛苦的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人和贵月学姐不再闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 C子酱真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.34,0:20:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 别随便摸女孩子的头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦~女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎么了 你再说一遍试试！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}暑假将始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}纵使一生也不会忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}难忘的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我想这…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}对大家来说也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}无论是欢喜抑或是悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}概其总总
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一生只此一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}彼夏伊始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}我识破了一夏学姐的真实身份了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}别说出来 不然我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.20,0:23:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\an1}哲郎死翘翘了
